        for(int i = 0; i < candies.length; i++) {
            int candy = candies[i];
            freq.put(candy, freq.get(candy) - 1);
            if(freq.get(candy) == 0) 
                freq.remove(candy);
            if(i >= k)
                freq.put(candies[i - k], freq.getOrDefault(candies[i - k], 0) + 1);
            if(i >= k - 1)
                result = Math.max(result, freq.size());
        }
        
        return result;
    }
